Package io.minAR.core

This package mainly contains the core classes involving the generation of internal file trees, analyzing and recreating existing file trees.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    NodeTree.NodeListener<T>
    A simple interface, lambda compatible, contains methods invoked upon every node while traversing through the NodeTree
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Analyzer
    Core class, involved in the creation of internal file trees, reading of data from the files and outputing the archive
    Extractor
    Core class, involved in retrieving and re-creating the internal file tree, and extraction of data from the nodes of the tree
    Hash  
    Node<T>  
    NodeTree<T>
    A tree of Node
